Target plan file path: docs/shopfloor/plans/42-add-github-oauth.md

<issue_body>
Users want to log in with GitHub.
</issue_body>

<spec_file_contents>
# Spec
Details here.
</spec_file_contents>

<previous_plan>

</previous_plan>

<review_feedback>
[]
